--- --- ---
Types
--- --- ---

---
Primitive types — numeric, bool, str
Sum types — variant
Product types — record
Generic/parameterized types — type T:
Dependent types — type size:
Sequence types — [.. T]
Record types — {.. T}
Function types — fn T: U
Type aliases — Foo = type: ...
Type inheritance/spread — ..BaseType
Structural/duck typing — TBD keyword
Protocol dispatch — abstract function types
Gradual typing — dynamic to static refinement
Refinement types — via pattern guards
Type inference — from usage and tests
---

---
Type hierarchy operators (<, >, <=, >=, >< on types, or/and for union/intersection types)
---

